{"title":"回家的路——一位台湾老兵历经磨难回到祖籍家乡","authors":["马福德"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":1,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"回家的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一位台湾老兵历经磨难回到祖籍家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马福德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着一道窄窄的海峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海那边就是我的家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在阿里山眺望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能看到村前的紫荆花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不遥远回家的路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年，却在梦里泡大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月沧桑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人为地扎起篱笆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山分半，月难圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有家难归，人在天涯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭望故乡泪如雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜思归盼彩霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤帆飘泊大海中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半生思念苦水洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱尝人间酸辛泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童心刻满伤心疤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走啊走，走不完的回家路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管路途多坎坷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痴心不改，心向华夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革春风吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦桥海上架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水流百转归大海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多年游子终回家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老手擦去思母泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举杯喝口蒙山茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家乡炕暖坐不住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看山看水看庄稼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美在心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路在脚下"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}